comment: /**  * Free the task slot with the given allocation id.  *  * @param allocationId to identify the slot to be freed  */
code: /**  * Free the task slot with the given allocation id.  *  * @param allocationId to identify the slot to be freed  */ void freeSlot(AllocationID allocationId).

comment: /**  * Timeout the task slot for the given allocation id. The timeout is identified by the given  * ticket to filter invalid timeouts out.  *  * @param allocationId identifying the task slot to be timed out  * @param ticket allowing to filter invalid timeouts out  */
code: /**  * Timeout the task slot for the given allocation id. The timeout is identified by the given  * ticket to filter invalid timeouts out.  *  * @param allocationId identifying the task slot to be timed out  * @param ticket allowing to filter invalid timeouts out  */ void timeoutSlot(AllocationID allocationId, UUID ticket).
